  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个关于教育系统的流程图，核心是StudentDB的状态流转。起点是判断节点c1，检查是否在StudentDB中。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，c1是菱形判断节点。那如果判断为No的话，流程去哪里？还有Yes分支呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c6",
        "c2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No分支直接到c6，也就是回到StudentDB的某个状态。Yes分支先到c2，c2也是个StudentDB相关的处理节点，然后再继续分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c6",
        "c2",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把c1、c2、c6都画成StudentDB相关的节点，c1用菱形，c2和c6用矩形。连接c1--No--c6。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c1",
        "c6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "c2之后要再判断一次，如果Yes就走到LMS_Portal，也就是c3和c4两个节点串联，最后回到c1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c1",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：c2--Yes--c3--c4--c1，这样形成一条循环路径回到判断节点。那c2的No分支呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "c1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "c2如果No，就走到ClassroomService，也就是c5，然后再到c6结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c5",
        "c6",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加c5作为ClassroomService节点，连接c2--No--c5--c6。现在c6有两个入口了，一个来自c1的No，一个来自c5。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c2",
        "c5",
        "c6",
        "c1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，c6是汇聚点。我注意到c3和c4都是LMS_Portal，但应该是串联执行的两个步骤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c3",
        "c4",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "这里有个问题，我之前把c3和c4都标成LMS_Portal，但c3应该是处理入口，c4是后续操作，虽然都是同一个系统，但节点要分开。我确认一下标签都用Education_LMS_Portal对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "c3",
        "c4"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，都是LMS_Portal系统的不同处理阶段。另外最后输出的时候，我们需要用mmdc生成svg和png两种格式，png要2400宽度透明背景。",
